newsitem.title: BRAZIL: Brazil's Telebras 7-mo net 1.573 bln reais.
newsitem.headline: Brazil's Telebras 7-mo net 1.573 bln reais.

text.p: Brazilian federally owned telecommunications giant Telebras released the following results for the first seven months of 1996.
Note: All figures are in Brazilian reais.
The company released the figures Wednesday night to Brazilian stock exchanges.
Full name of company is Telecomunicacoes Brasileiras SA
